    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>As reported by Rafael Hengles:</p>

<p>I had a problem sending mails through a Microsoft ESMTP server, and I
discovered that on the RSET command, it returned 220 instead of the expected
by ZF, 250. I hacked it to "$this-&gt;_expect(array(250,220));" and now it
works. Anybody knows a better solution or why does this happen?</p>

